{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Homepage Theme","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"MStore Pro - Complete React Native template for e-commerce","meta_description":"Professional Mobile Store Solution for your business – supports to convert your current WooCommerce website to mobile store app easily","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"mstore","toc":null,"keywords":["mstore","mstore pro","woocommerce app","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"how-to-update-to-new9-homepage-layout\"><a href=\"#how-to-update-to-new9-homepage-layout\" aria-label=\"how to update to new9 homepage layout permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to update to new+9 Homepage layout.</h2>\n<p>Since Mstore 3.7.0 you can change to many kinds of UI homepage, by open <em>src/common/AppConfigTheme</em> and copy the content of the theme to override to <em>src/common/AppConfig.json</em></p>\n<p>Some <strong>layout</strong> support for the HorionLayout object: the component layout, support for following type layouts: <em>circleCategory, bannerImage,bannerSlider</em>, <em>featureProducts, threeColumn, twoColumn, bannerHigh, card, simple.</em></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-default-theme\"><a href=\"#1-default-theme\" aria-label=\"1 default theme permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Default Theme</h3>\n<p>The layout content below components. It’s possible to add new component via CeBuilder or manually edit the AppConfig.json.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*IuhEWqENa0s8mf4PFeE-Mw.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Circle category</li>\n<li>Banner High</li>\n<li>2 Banner Image</li>\n<li>Three Columns list view</li>\n<li>Two Columns list view</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-banner-image\"><a href=\"#2-banner-image\" aria-label=\"2 banner image permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Banner Image</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*zCITotLraTjwFCVGVbq8kQ.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>The layout content most of the Banner Image components and link to website category Id.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"imageBanner\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://mstore.io/images/shoes.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"column\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  \n  <span class=\"token string\">\"height\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">130</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"layout\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"bannerImage\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \n  <span class=\"token string\">\"category\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>imageBanner</strong>: te URL link to an online image</li>\n<li><strong>column</strong>: to let the app know to render as the column view</li>\n<li><strong>height</strong>: the height of the image banner</li>\n<li><strong>category</strong>: the Id of the category of the WooCommerce site</li>\n<li><strong>imageMode</strong>: the mode of the image render, similar to the React native.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-banner-image-and-vertical-two-column-list\"><a href=\"#3-banner-image-and-vertical-two-column-list\" aria-label=\"3 banner image and vertical two column list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Banner Image and Vertical Two Column list</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*9C_BZx35xDUv5DWzC68VaA.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Banner Image</li>\n<li>Circle Category</li>\n<li>Three Columns list view</li>\n<li>Vertical Two columns with lazy load</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-banner-image-and-vertical-three-column-list\"><a href=\"#4-banner-image-and-vertical-three-column-list\" aria-label=\"4 banner image and vertical three column list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Banner Image and Vertical Three Column list</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*jqEzDohixE5Tkzt9vFn9MA.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Banner Image</li>\n<li>Circle Category</li>\n<li>Three Columns list view</li>\n<li>Vertical Three columns list with lazy load</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"5-banner-slider-image-and-vertical-cart-list\"><a href=\"#5-banner-slider-image-and-vertical-cart-list\" aria-label=\"5 banner slider image and vertical cart list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Banner Slider Image and Vertical Cart list</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*qWOWMAgpMtnvYO3CHXg_Yg.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Banner Slider Image</li>\n<li>Circle Category</li>\n<li>Horizontal Three Columns list view</li>\n<li>Vertical Card list with lazy load</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"6-banner-and-vertical-list\"><a href=\"#6-banner-and-vertical-list\" aria-label=\"6 banner and vertical list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. Banner and Vertical List</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*fNP1BwzHjEB-bGyTOaykzA.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Circle Category</li>\n<li>Horizontal list banner</li>\n<li>Vertical banner with a simple list</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"7-banner-high-and-vertical-two-columns-list\"><a href=\"#7-banner-high-and-vertical-two-columns-list\" aria-label=\"7 banner high and vertical two columns list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7. Banner High and Vertical Two Columns List</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*Nbc53YbLqUK6S-AlyVSTyw.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Circle Category</li>\n<li>Banner High</li>\n<li>Vertical banner with two column list</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"8-banner-high-and-vertical-card-list\"><a href=\"#8-banner-high-and-vertical-card-list\" aria-label=\"8 banner high and vertical card list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>8. Banner High and Vertical Card List</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*NdV9xhnznUXarD4BaujBfg.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Circle Category</li>\n<li>Banner High</li>\n<li>Vertical banner with Card list</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"9-banner-and-category-list\"><a href=\"#9-banner-and-category-list\" aria-label=\"9 banner and category list permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>9. Banner and Category List</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*cZFPuU3fdieV0NO5H3dN2Q.gif\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Banner list</li>\n<li>Circle Category with 4 columns view</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/mstore/home-theme/"},"timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"How to update to new+9 Homepage layout. Since Mstore 3.7.0 you can change to many kinds of UI homepage, by open  src/common/AppConfigTheme…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/documents/inspireui-documents/docs/content/mstore/home-theme.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/mstore/home-theme/"}}